2  ¦  21  ¦  0001020000  ¦  000102  ¦  000102  ¦  3  𝄀
3  ¦  30  ¦  null  ¦  null  ¦  null  ¦  -1  𝄀
4  ¦  41  ¦  0000000000  ¦    ¦    ¦  0
data branch diff t_branch against t_src output count;
➤ COUNT(*)[-5,0,0]  𝄀
